        "text": "Youths oppress my people, women rule over them. My people, your guides lead you astray; they turn you from the path."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Childish leaders oppress my people, and women rule over them. O my people, your leaders mislead you; they send you down the wrong road."
      }
